{"data": [{"id": "4741898", "title": "Simon Property Group Remains A Valuable Investment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lululemon store entrance\" data-id=\"1169870817\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Simon Property Group, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPG\" title=\"Simon Property Group, Inc.\">SPG</a></span>) is one of the largest American REITs with a market capitalization of almost $60 billion and a yield of almost 5%. The company saw its share price pummeled initially after COVID-19, but it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741898-simon-property-group-remains-a-valuable-investment", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 02:29:52"}, {"id": "4741902", "title": "Okta, Inc. 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Okta, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106011\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741902-okta-inc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 02:03:32"}, {"id": "4741893", "title": "TMSL: Multi-Factor ETF Off To A Good Start", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Racers at start line on track\" data-id=\"77930917\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Chris Ryan/OJO Images via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h3><strong>TMSL strategy</strong></h3> <p><b>T. Rowe Price Small-Mid Cap ETF</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TMSL\" title=\"T. Rowe Price Small-Mid Cap ETF\">TMSL</a></span>) is an actively managed, multifactor ETF launched on 6/14/2023 with an objective of long-term capital growth. It has 276 holdings, a 30-day SEC yield of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741893-tmsl-multi-factor-etf-off-to-a-good-start", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 02:00:45"}, {"id": "4741891", "title": "United States Steel's Plunge Represents A Great Buying Opportunity", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Old Iron Plate Embossed With \"MADE IN USA\"' data-id=\"184967527\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">joecicak</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December 3 ended up being a pretty bad day for shareholders of <strong>United States Steel Corporation</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/X\" title=\"United States Steel Corporation\">X</a></span>). Shares of the company fell over 8% after <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357389-trump-again-vows-to-block-us-steel-sale-to-nippon-steel\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357389-trump-again-vows-to-block-us-steel-sale-to-nippon-steel\" target=\"_blank\">news broke</a> over night that President-elect Donald Trump has reaffirmed his opposition</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741891-united-states-steels-plunge-represents-a-great-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 01:45:38"}, {"id": "4741886", "title": "Agios Pharmaceuticals: A Long Overdue Follow Up", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Life Science Investing\" data-id=\"155151969\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"715px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bill Oxford</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It has been just over two years since our last look at <strong>Agios Pharmaceuticals (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AGIO\" title=\"Agios Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">AGIO</a></span>)</strong>. We concluded that <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4550913-agios-pharmaceuticals-big-year-on-horizon\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4550913-agios-pharmaceuticals-big-year-on-horizon\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>article</strong></a> by saying the stock merited a \"watch item\" position at that time and that at some point we would follow up on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741886-agios-pharmaceuticals-a-long-overdue-follow-up", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 01:21:07"}, {"id": "4741885", "title": "Intel: Pat's Away -- Reiterating Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Spotlight on microphone stand on stage\" data-id=\"200488260-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Adam Taylor/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Intel Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) stock shot up after news of now ex-CEO Pat Gelsinger's abrupt <a href=\"https://www.intc.com/news-events/press-releases/detail/1719/intel-announces-retirement-of-ceo-pat-gelsinger\" rel=\"nofollow\">retirement</a> amid what looks like internal disputes about INTC's strategic direction and lackluster performance under Gelsinger. Our take</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200488260/image_200488260.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741885-intel-pat-away-reiterating-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 01:19:05"}, {"id": "4741882", "title": "Verano Holdings: Rare Entry Point For Long Term Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Herbal Cannabis In A Jar In A Cannabis Shop In Thailand\" data-id=\"2075431460\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">urbazon/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4675584-verano-holdings-temporary-setbacks-potential-long-term-gains\">previous analysis </a>covering Verano Holdings Corp. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VRNO:CA\" title=\"Verano Holdings Corp.\">VRNO:CA</a></span>)(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">OTCQX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VRNOF\" title=\"Verano Holdings Corp.\">VRNOF</a></span>), despite reporting positive financial results for Q4 2023, the company's stock price declined by nearly 10% due to its delay in filing 10-K with the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075431460/image_2075431460.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741882-verano-holdings-rare-entry-point-for-long-term-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 01:10:56"}, {"id": "4741888", "title": "VEA ETF: America's Allies Are Faltering", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aged style world map, paper texture background\" data-id=\"175482512\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">sankai/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Investment thesis:</strong> The Vanguard FTSE Developed Markets Index Fund ETF Shares (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VEA\" title=\"Vanguard FTSE Developed Markets Index Fund ETF Shares\">VEA</a></span>) is a diverse fund that covers foreign developed markets, with over 3,900 individual stocks comprising the fund. It serves as broad exposure to America's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175482512/image_175482512.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741888-vea-etf-americas-allies-are-faltering", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 01:01:58"}, {"id": "4741879", "title": "Coupang's Growth Story Persists Amid South Korean Market Unrest", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coupang headquarters in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1312190830\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4183px\" height=\"2353px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Coupang, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CPNG\" title=\"Coupang, Inc.\">CPNG</a></span>) stock, termed \u201cthe Amazon of South Korea,\u201d dropped today along with most South Korean stocks. The <a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2024/12/03/asia/south-korea-martial-law-intl/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">declaration of martial law</a> (now <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4359443-south-korean-won-plummets-against-the-us-dollar-after-president-declares-emergency\">in doubt</a>) by South Korean President Yoon Suk Yeol, even</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312190830/image_1312190830.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741879-coupang-growth-story-persists-amid-south-korean-market-unrest", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 00:56:37"}, {"id": "4741892", "title": "Pure Storage, Inc. 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Pure Storage, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106010\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741892-pure-storage-inc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 00:52:48"}]}